# NAME: BitComet_Direct_Optimized
# AUTHOR: AI & User Patch
# 作用：强行将 BT/PT 下载的 Tracker、Peer、种子网络及彗星官方底层锁死在直连，防止机场封号或限速

# ==================== 1. 规则优化：精确追踪器与统计关键字 (防误伤) ====================
# 替换掉范围过大的 generic keywords，防止误伤 Google/CDN 及其他服务
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,tracker
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,announce
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,tracker-stat
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,peer-stat
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stats-download
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,stat-cdn

# ==================== 2. PT / BT 常用站点与核心框架域名 ====================
# PT 站点通用前端/API/Tracker
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,m-team.cc
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chdbits.co
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hdsky.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ourbits.club
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pthome.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hdchina.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,nexusphp.org

# 境外顶级 PT 站点防御线
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,passthepopcorn
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,broadcasthe.net
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,privatehd
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,audiences

# ==================== 3. 补充 BitComet 及主流 BT 客户端关联域名 ====================
# 彗星网络、长效种子网络、电驴插件
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cometnetwork.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitcomet.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bitcomet.net

# 其他主流 BT 客户端 (qBittorrent / Transmission / uTorrent)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,utorrent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,qbittorrent.org
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,transmissionbt.com

# 公共 Tracker 常用域名后缀
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,opentracker.i2p.rocks
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openbittorrent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,publicbt.com

# ==================== 4. 官方底层握手服务器 IP 自治域 ====================
# 彗星官方登录和全球用户交换（PEX）最核心的境外机房服务器 IP 段
IP-CIDR,62.210.122.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,91.121.144.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,188.165.230.0/24,no-resolve
IP-CIDR,198.251.81.0/24,no-resolve
